            "id": 6011105,
            "title": "金像電接單熱又有新產能挹注  5月營收46.84億元再創新高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>PCB 廠金像電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2368:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2368\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2368-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日公布最新營收資訊，2025 年 5 月營收以 46.84 億元創下的新高紀錄，月增 1.79%，年增 38.98%，2025 年 1-5 月營收 212.42 億元，年增 38.89%，金像電在新產能開出挹注之下，今年 2 月起單月營收持續創新高。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011105%2Fl%2F17f0ce509c32758741aa9d48404e3f52.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">金像電5月營收創歷史新高，新產能開出有利再拉升產值。(圖：金像電提供)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金像電 2024 年每股純益達 11.54 元，董事會通過擬配發現金股利 6 元，配息率約 52%，其獲利及配息，在 PCB 族群都屬於前段班。今年同步在逐季有產能開出，有利在 AI 伺服器的訂單及出貨量再向上提升。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>同時，金像電包括第二季的蘇州廠、下半年的泰國廠，都有機會再提升金像電單月產值再向上，並有利於獲利的成長。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>金像電 2025 年第一季稅後純益 17.53 億元，每股純益達 3.6 元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
