            "title": "5月就業報告發布前 10年期美債殖利率下滑",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國公債殖利率周五 (6 日) 有所回落，投資人正熱切期待 5 月非農業就業報告，以評估美國經濟的健康狀況。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011106%2Fl%2Fa49dc660fab32420288666f0db5975b7.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">10年期美債殖利率下滑。（圖：REUTERS/TPG）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美東時間 7:26，10 年期美國公債殖利率下跌 1.2 個基點至 4.383%。2 年期美國公債殖利率下跌 0.8 個基點至 3.916%；而 30 年期美國公債殖利率下跌 1.6 個基點至 4.868%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1 個基點等於 0.01 個百分點。殖利率與價格走勢相反。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國勞動市場最新數據將於美東時間上午 8:30 公布。接受《<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊</a>》調查的經濟學家預測 5 月就業將增加 12.5 萬個。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>如果數據低於預期，將是一系列令人失望的數據中的最新一個；這些數據包括高於預期的每周失業救濟金申請人數和服務業活動疲軟。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>市場正在密切關注川普總統關稅政策的影響，預計今年經濟成長將大幅放緩。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
